data.description: Price Reduced!! Seller motivated!! LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!   Welcome to the Park Creek community located in the heart of Riverview, where this impeccably maintained, 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2-car garage home built by Holiday Homes awaits you to become its new owner. As you step inside, you'll discover to your immediate right a spacious bedroom or it can be used as a home office. As you continue entering this beautiful property you will find a generously sized open concept that is combined with a dining room, living room and kitchen. The kitchen comes complete with appliances, granite countertops, stunning backsplash, 42” cabinets, a convenient breakfast bar, and a pantry with ample storage. The seamless transition to the screened in patio is a delightful space for outdoor dining or enjoying the natural beauty of the surroundings. The split bedroom plan ensures privacy and comfort, with three generously sized bedrooms. The primary suite offers a large bedroom that exudes elegance and charm. The walk-in closet provides ample storage space. In addition, the master bathroom boasts two sinks, a glass shower, and a relaxing garden tub, creating a private oasis for unwinding after a long day.  This home is fully equipped, with all appliances, water softener, sprinkling system and has been treated annually for termites. Washer and dryer are negotiable. The HOA dues include Wi-Fi internet service and cable. The HOA amenities enhance your lifestyle with access to a resort-style pool with cabanas, a clubhouse/pavilion, walking trails, and a shaded playground for the little ones. The home is conveniently located near shops, restaurants, hospitals, and more, this home offers a lifestyle of comfort and convenience. Don't miss out – call today to arrange your showing!
